text: Sibilla Di Vincenzo (born 22 January 1983) is a female racewalker, who won a silver medal with the Italian team at the European Race Walking Cup. ==Achievements== {| class="wikitable" width=50% style="font-size:90%; text- align:center;" !Year !!Competition !!Venue !!Position !!Event!!Performance!!Notes |- | rowspan=1| 2010 | rowspan=1 align=left|European Championships | rowspan=1 align=left| Barcelona | | 20 km | no time | |} ==National titles== She won nine time the national championships. * Italian Athletics Championships ** 5 km walk: 2005, 2008, 2009, 2010 ** 20 km walk: 2010, 2016 * Italian Athletics Indoor Championships ** 3000 m walk: 2010, 2011, 2016 ==References== ==External links== * * Sibilla Di Vincenzo at FIDAL Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female racewalkers
